      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点叫User Query。那第一步是不是要先判断需不需要澄清？有些查询可能信息不完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check",
        "Need Clarification"
