      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，加个Limit节点，判断Asked是否小于2次。如果是，回到Check重新判断；超过两次就强制继续。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Limit",
        "Asked < 2 times",
